show.title: Got You! Mr. Always Right

show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा

show.description: When Jane's ex and rival invite her to their engagement just to humiliate her, she hires a fake husband — charming driver Mike. What she doesn’t know: Mike is secretly wealthy and already knows who she is. As Jane steps into high society, love, jealousy, and family secrets collide in a whirlwind of drama.
